asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Space "Belle" Cowgirl
description:
Myra Maybelle Shirley Reed Starr was born in Carthage, Missouri, in 1848. 
Frank and Jesse James's gang hid out at her family's farm when she was a kid, and from then on she was hooked on the outlaw life. Her husband Jim Reed shot a man, causing both to be on the run, robbing banks and counterfeiting. 

Starr, known to wear feathers in her hair, buckskins, and a pistol on each hip, was shot in the back while riding in 1889...it's still unclear if her death was accidental -- or something more sinister..

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: NAKITA
description:
She's mysterious, keen and frank. This isn't surprising considering for someone with her ugly past.

She was born and grew up in a poor family far from the Great Tree, she lived free of worries until she was about 6 years old, but at that point life changed drastically.

She destroyed someone's life accidentally during a mycelium outage and was headed for a life of crime. With the help of a suspicious stranger she was able to survive in a bleak world. With her courage and wits, she managed to battle the elements and train to perfection, turning her into the elite athlete she is today. 

After finally turning her life around, she now works in an art gallery as a curator, the perfect cover for her real passion as a professional assassin focused on ridding the world of bad actors intent on damaging the planet. By doing so, she hopes to find some form of redemption and finally find peace of mind she has never had.
